intent.user_query: Can we identify any seasonal trends in sales (e.g., monthly sales patterns)?

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT EXTRACT(MONTH FROM OrderDate) AS OrderMonth, SUM(OrderTotal) AS TotalSales FROM fitness_db.Orders GROUP BY EXTRACT(MONTH FROM OrderDate) ORDER BY OrderMonth;

arguments.sql: SELECT EXTRACT(MONTH FROM OrderDate) AS OrderMonth, SUM(OrderTotal) AS TotalSales FROM fitness_db.Orders GROUP BY EXTRACT(MONTH FROM OrderDate) ORDER BY OrderMonth;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
